<p class="ql-align-center">合影留念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201020/53cb3bf2bc584f55894140be345ac698.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201020/8b068c9082354e96b925f8bcfa30f30a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
